TI  - Characteristics of the early secondary succession after landslides in a broad-leaved deciduous forest in the south Minshan Mountains
PY  - 2017
T2  - Forest Ecology and Management
VL  - 405
SP  - 238
EP  - 245
DO  - 10.1016/j.foreco.2017.09.020
