AB  - The proceedings contain 30 papers. The topics discussed include: the impact of landuse and the relationship between NDVI on the bird species richness in Sukmajaya District, Depok; flood deposits characterization in Citarum Riverbank Area in Bandung Regency, West Java, Indonesia; distribution of peak ground acceleration in Pandeglang Regency, Banten; nanocomposite of cellulose and magnetite-magnesia as catalyst for biodiesel from coconut oil; thermal properties of kenaf fiber-based nanocellulose reinforced polyurethane composites; the validation of water quality parameter algorithm using Landsat 8 and Sentinel-2 image in Palabuhanratu Bay; vegetative conservation of landslide prone areas in the Cidadap Watershed Area, Sukabumi Regency; lobster aquaculture location selection based on oceanographic conditions using remote sensing (case study: Ciletuh Bay, Sukabumi, Indonesia); and estimation of flash flood loss level in Banjaririgasi Village, Lebakgedong Sub-district, Lebak Regency, Banten.
