TI  - Determination of Correction Coefficients of Wu's Model of Root Cohesion Based on Successive Fracture Process
PY  - 2017
T2  - Linye Kexue/Scientia Silvae Sinicae
VL  - 53
IS  - 11
SP  - 170
EP  - 178
DO  - 10.11707/j.1001-7488.20171120
