AB  - The proceedings contain 80 papers. The topics discussed include: designing of municipal solid waste (MSW) treatment plant in Onggomertan Village, Yogyakarta; identification of slip surface based on geoelectrical dipoledipole in the landslides hazardous area of Gedangsari District, Gunungkidul Regency, province of Daerah Istimewa Yogyakarta, Indonesia; treatment of brackish groundwater by zeolite filtration in Sumur Tua Wonocolo, Kedewan, Bojonegoro, East Java; the content of heavy metals in vegetables in the hydrothermal alteration rocks  Boto Wonogiri Central Java; Geology at Beruang Kanan, Central Kalimantan, Indonesia; and an initial study to investigate generating hydrocarbon potential of tertiary coals from Balikpapan and Pulaubalang Formations in Lower Kutai Basin, East Kalimantan, Indonesia.
