AB  - This study was conducted on a landside mass at Xiejiadian Village, Lonemenshan Town, caused by Wenchuan earthquake. Based on 5 years' permanent plot surveys, plant community composition, species diversity, and biomass were analyzed. The results showed that: from 2008 to 2013, the species composition of plant communities has been in abundance; species diversity indices are high; the plant community has a big biomass already. © 2014 Taylor & Francis Group, London.
